dc_title_s: Geologic map of the Las Yeguas Ranch quadrangle, San Luis Obispo and Kern counties, California
dc_description_s: geology by T.W. Dibblee Jr. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Las Yeguas Ranch, CA 1959, photoinspected 1973, AMS 2054 IV NW -- Series V895." "First printing, October 2006." Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology.
dc_publisher_s: Santa Barbara Museum of Natural History
